To estimate QBI, calculate
1. Expected business income for {taxyear}
2. Minus ordinary business expenses (like rent, supplies, and employee benefits
3. Minus self-employment-related deductions (like self-employed health insurance premium,s contributions to self-employed retirement plans, and half of your self-employment tax)
Estimated qualified business income for you/you and your spouse for {TY}
